<LI>Decrease Hitpoints by 6 (L1) to 7 (L2)</ul></font><br>Damage/mana effeciency: <font class=spell>0.46 (L1) to 0.54 (L2)<i> per target</i></font><br><br>Whizbang's Notes: <ul><font class=spell>This is our first Point Blank Area of Effect spell. The later spells in this line are what wizards use for AoE groups: The spells hit unlimited targets, all at once. Having said that, Numbing Cold is unlikely to kill any opponents, even with several first level wizards casting it together. An interesting spell to play around with, but probably not a staple of wizards at this level.</font></ul></ul>
